<li>Start with a nucleus:  Fe<sup>57</sup> : emits a photon (14.4 keV)
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>There is a nuclear recoil to conserve momentum.. Takes away some energy
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Photon energy slightly less than the energy gap</li>
</ul></li>
<li>Consequence: This means that iron foil is transparent to its own radiation.</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p>
